{{wikipedia}}
==English==

===Etymology===
From [[share]] + [[ware]] a contraction of [[software]]; Coined by [[w:Bob Wallace|Bob Wallace]]

===Noun===
'''shareware''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

#{{cattag|Computing}}: A type of [[software]] that is [[distribute]]d without payment but is limited in any combination of [[functionality]], [[availability]], or [[convenience]].

====Translations====
*Chinese: [[共享软件]]/[[共享軟體]] (gongxiang-ruanjian)
*Japanese: [[シェアウェア]] (sheawea)
*Korean: [[쉐어웨어]] (sweeoweeo)
*Turkish: [[deneme yazılımı]]

